Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,良介！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没能赶上…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 掉下来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,良介…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有死啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没 结果不还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:00:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小美菜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.33,0:01:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定会拯救良介的 用美菜所拥有的特异者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.87,0:01:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,良介会得救的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.71,0:01:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小美菜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜讬你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也麻烦大家了
Comment: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OP
